t for Crows-Chapter 8\">Chapter 8</a>, Jaime I.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Ragot6.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-10\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Ragot6.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_10-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Game_of_Thrones\" title=\"A Game of Thrones\">A Game of Thrones</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Game_of_Thrones-Chapter_6\" title=\"A Game of Thrones-Chapter 6\">Chapter 6</a>, Catelyn II.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rssm1183.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-11\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rssm1183.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_11-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a href=\"/index.php/So_Spake_Martin\" title=\"So Spake Martin\">So Spake Martin</a>: <i><a class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.westeros.org/Citadel/SSM/Entry/1183\">Concerning Dorne</a></i> (October 28, 2001).</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rssm1193.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-12\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rssm1193.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_12-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a href=\"/index.php/So_Spake_Martin\" title=\"So Spake Martin\">So Spake Martin</a>: <i><a class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.westeros.org/Citadel/SSM/Entry/1193\">Valyria-related Subjects</a></i> (January 1, 2002).</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-13\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-13\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a href=\"/index.php/Not_A_Blog\" title=\"Not A Blog\">Not A Blog</a>: <a class=\"external text\" href=\"https://georgerrmartin.com/notablog/2018/11/16/farewell-to-a-marvel/\">Farewell to a Marvel</a>, November 16, 2018</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-14\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-14\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\">Citadel: <a class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.westeros.org/Citadel/FAQ/Entry/